Inform the relevant field with the commencement date (day, month, year) for the interposed entity election. In these circumstances, the election commencement time will be the later of the earliest time from which the family control test was passed continuously until the end of the full income year eg. 2007-2008 and the beginning of the day specified for an election to be made.
